BBQ Pork Tacos

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyquicktacosBBQ

Description

Deliciously tender BBQ pork served in soft tortillas topped with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 1 lb
  • bbq sauce: 1 cup
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime: 1, cut into wedges
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
